' Domain: Finance
' Scope: Expense creation and expense ledger query use cases.
' Sources: services/finance-service/src/main/java/com/fern/services/finance/api/FinanceController.java; docs/frontend-readiness.md.
' Note: derived from source code.

@startuml
title FERN Use Case - Finance
left to right direction

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor #F7FAFC
  BorderColor #2B4C7E
  ArrowColor #425466
  FontColor #16324F
}
skinparam actor {
  BorderColor #425466
  FontColor #16324F
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF8E1
  BorderColor #C28A00
}

actor "Tài chính\nFinance" as ACT_FINANCE
actor "Quản trị hệ thống\nAdmin" as ACT_ADMIN
ACT_ADMIN --|> ACT_FINANCE

rectangle "FERN ERP Platform\nFinance" as SYS_FIN {
  usecase "UC-FIN-01\nGhi nhận chi phí vận hành\nCreate Operating Expense" as UC_FIN_01
  usecase "UC-FIN-02\nGhi nhận chi phí khác\nCreate Other Expense" as UC_FIN_02
  usecase "UC-FIN-03\nXem chi tiết chi phí\nGet Expense Detail" as UC_FIN_03
  usecase "UC-FIN-04\nTra cứu chi phí\nList Expenses" as UC_FIN_04
}

ACT_FINANCE --> UC_FIN_01
ACT_FINANCE --> UC_FIN_02
ACT_FINANCE --> UC_FIN_03
ACT_FINANCE --> UC_FIN_04

note right of SYS_FIN
  derived from source code
  Primary source:
  - FinanceController.java
  Supporting source:
  - docs/frontend-readiness.md
  Current frontend contract is admin-only.
end note

@enduml
